{"tid":2100774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［何超貧現身］靈堂外自稱是何鴻燊親女 周女士：一出世俾人抱去山旮旯","createTime":"2020-07-09T09:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T10:31:34.000Z","uid":105567,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ace2ed6ec7a80ee2ff0442333e6df51033c7cf7b","tid":2100774,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:48:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200709/LCZQXATAJ5DS7TOAXMDE7YXDL4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200709%2FLCZQXATAJ5DS7TOAXMDE7YXDL4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmqDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=9c94d2ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200709%2FLCZQXATAJ5DS7TOAXMDE7YXDL4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=ebefb050\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200709/LCZQXATAJ5DS7TOAXMDE7YXDL4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n何家四房親屬今日齊集位於北角的香港殯儀館，為賭王何鴻燊舉行設靈，並於下午4時進行公祭，雖然距離公祭尚有一段時間，但殯儀館門外已陸續聚集前來弔唁的市民。當記者在現場和其中一個身穿大紅大紫鮮色旗袍、倚在欄杆等候入場的周姓女士傾談時，對方竟然自稱是何鴻燊親生女兒，更說自己姓周而非姓何，是由於小時候被人抱走關係。<br />\n<br />\n其後，有個自稱是周女士丈夫的譚姓男士，聲稱自己是譚詠麟細佬，他又指自己因為得閒，才陪太太前來向賭王致祭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_UpsLT9XNSwayRUjJYwgssjPQ24=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/44KO63UNM54JGVMBBAD3QFWNBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_UpsLT9XNSwayRUjJYwgssjPQ24%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-a